<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h3 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Examining the 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        lining and interior details
      </span>
    </h3>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      The lining and interior details of a Louis Vuitton handbag can also reveal its authenticity. Here are some things to look for:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The lining of an authentic Louis Vuitton handbag is typically made of high-quality fabric, such as cotton or silk. This luxurious material is smooth to the touch and adds to the overall elegance of the bag.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The lining should be smooth and even, with no wrinkles or creases. Any irregularities in the lining can indicate a counterfeit product.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The interior pockets and compartments should be neatly stitched and have a smooth, even finish. The precision of the interior construction reflects Louis Vuitton’s meticulous craftsmanship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The Louis Vuitton logo should be printed or embroidered on the lining, and the font should be consistent with the brand’s signature style. This branding is a key indicator of authenticity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The interior details, such as the stitching and seams, should be precise and even, with no loose threads or uneven stitches. The interior construction should mirror the exterior in terms of quality and attention to detail.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Three text columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns article_three-text-columns rebranding-wider-section-bottom",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}